  <p class="expanded-intro">I’ve had a look, there are plenty of dogs on there near where you live. You’ll have to register on their website to see what’s available and to start getting matched with a dog. You can do this for free with basic membership and upgrade if you find dogs that you want to walk.</p>
  <header>
